name: Rose Earrings
description: I love these rose charms – they are so detailed! These pretty roses are strung onto sterling silver ear wires. The roses measures 7mm across. Click on arrows below image to see more pictures. Have an Etsy account? You can purchase this item at GUGAW’s etsy store

name: Hessonite and swallow earrings - sterling silver
description:
The hessonite briolletes as so pretty! They have an amazing shine to them, almost a glitter. A deep red/orange shade perfect for autumn and winter. The hessonite stones have been wrapped with sterling silver wire and adorned with lovely swallow charms. The ear wires are made of sterling silver.

	The earrings measure approximately 3cm in length from the ear wire.

	Click on arrows below image to see more pictures.

name: Red Jasper and Filigree Butterfly Necklace
description:
This piece of red jade is gorgeous! It’s a really large piece with beautiful colourings throughout. To start, the red is such a rich colour, and there are lovely brown dapples which can be seen in between the antenna of the butterfly. The butterfly itself is brass filigree, which has been securely wrapped around the jasper. The pendant has then been strung onto a vintage style brass chain, which is adorned with a brass bird with spread wings.

	The red jasper pendant measures approximately 5cm in length, the chain measures 68cm including hte brass bird.

	This item comes gift wrapped in a kraft box.

	Click on arrows below image to see more pictures.

name: Little Apple Green - sterling silver necklace
description:
Yummy juicy green apple! This small apple charm is so pretty and delicate – such a bright and crisp green. The detail on the leaf is very beautifully etched. This little apple is strung onto a fine link sterling silver chain to compliment the design of the apple

	The charm is enamelled pewter, measuring 7mm x 12mm. The sterling silver chain measures approximately 46cm (18 inches)
